   Duke J 1975 pp 6 [PH, TEMP, RAIN]
   Maas E 1990 pp 278
   Sims D 1993 (pers. comm.)
   Rice R 1990 pp 307-308 [TEXT, FER, TEMP, RAIN]
   Siemonsma J 1993 pp 64-68 [TEMP, RAIN, DRA, TEXT, PH, PHO]

